  {"id":"ch2-tcop-006","stem":"TCOP 中 APM（应用性能监控）的核心能力是？","options":[{"label":"A","text":"自动发现应用拓扑，监控接口响应时间、错误率和吞吐量"},{"label":"B","text":"仅监控CPU使用率"},{"label":"C","text":"管理应用代码版本"},{"label":"D","text":"自动修复应用bug"}],"answer":["A"],"type":"single","chapter":2,"subChapter":"ch2-tcop","tags":["TCOP","APM","应用监控"],"analysis":"APM（Application Performance Monitoring）通过在应用中植入探针自动采集：1)服务拓扑（微服务间调用关系）；2)接口级性能（响应时间/错误率/QPS）；3)慢请求详情和异常堆栈。帮助快速定位性能瓶颈和故障根因。","wikiUrl":"https://angelsnow1129.github.io/TCCPWiki/chapter2/2.17_%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E4%BA%91%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%82%E6%B5%8B%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0/","difficulty":2},
  {"id":"ch2-tcop-007","stem":"可观测平台中 SLI/SLO/SLA 的关系是？","options":[{"label":"A","text":"SLI 是可量化的服务指标，SLO 是目标值，SLA 是与客户的正式承诺"},{"label":"B","text":"三者含义完全相同"},{"label":"C","text":"SLA 是内部指标，SLO 是外部承诺"},{"label":"D","text":"只有SLA有实际意义"}],"answer":["A"],"type":"single","chapter":2,"subChapter":"ch2-tcop","tags":["TCOP","SLI","SLO","SLA"],"analysis":"SLI（Service Level Indicator）：可量化的服务质量指标（如可用性99.95%、P99延迟<200ms）。SLO（Service Level Objective）：SLI的内部目标值。SLA（Service Level Agreement）：与客户签订的正式服务承诺，通常包含违约赔偿。SLO应严于SLA留有余量。","wikiUrl":"https://angelsnow1129.github.io/TCCPWiki/chapter2/2.17_%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E4%BA%91%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%82%E6%B5%8B%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0/","difficulty":2},
  {"id":"ch2-tcop-008","stem":"Grafana 在可观测体系中的角色是什么？","options":[{"label":"A","text":"数据可视化平台，将 Prometheus/CLS 等数据源以图表和 Dashboard 形式展示"},{"label":"B","text":"数据采集Agent"},{"label":"C","text":"日志存储系统"},{"label":"D","text":"代码部署工具"}],"answer":["A"],"type":"single","chapter":2,"subChapter":"ch2-tcop","tags":["TCOP","Grafana","可视化"],"analysis":"Grafana是开源的数据可视化平台，支持对接Prometheus、CLS、MySQL等多种数据源，通过丰富的图表类型（折线图、热力图、表格等）构建实时监控Dashboard。TCOP内置Grafana服务，免去自建维护成本。","wikiUrl":"https://angelsnow1129.github.io/TCCPWiki/chapter2/2.17_%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E4%BA%91%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%82%E6%B5%8B%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0/","difficulty":1}
